id: NEED-visual-grounding
kind: need
name: VLM reasons from image space, not pre-encoded coordinates
status: draft
description: The VLM must identify features and navigation targets by reading the map image, not by recalling coordinate math that small models perform unreliably. This drives the pixel-coordinate output schema and the prompt design that strips named landmarks and coordinate answer keys.
derives_from: CON-autonomous-mission-loop
validated_by: VAL-mission-002-boundary-pattern
derived_by: REQ-pixel-coordinate-output
